\c 14
\s Upenzi nekuipa kwemunhu
\p Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Benzi rakati mumoyo maro: Hakuna Mwari. Vakaora, vakaita mabasa anonyangadza; hapana anoita zvakanaka.
\v 2 Jehovha ari kudenga, akatarira pasi kuvana vavanhu, kuti aone kana akachenjera aripo, anotsvaka Mwari.
\v 3 Vakatsauka vese, vakasvibiswa pamwe chete; hapana anoita zvakanaka, kunyange nomumwe.
\v 4 Ko vaiti vese vezvakaipa havana zivo here? Ivo vanodya vanhu vangu sezvavanodya chingwa, vasingadani kuna Jehovha.
\v 5 Vakange vachitya zvikuru ipapo; nokuti Mwari anogara parudzi rwavakarurama.
\v 6 Munonyadzisa zano romurombo, asi Jehovha ndiye utiziro hwake.
\p
\v 7 Dai kuponeswa kwaIsraeri kwaibva paZiyoni! Kana Jehovha achidzosa vanhu vake pakutapwa, ipapo Jakove achafarisisa kwazvo, naIsraeri achafara.
